Package: declustr
Title: Analysis of Spatial Sample Clustering and Declustering
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Trueman", email = "amt4158@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Various functions for analysing point patterns and calculating 
    decluster weights using various methods. Current implimentation is for 2D
    samples only.
